properties.text:
[b]Keyboard controls:[/b]
[color=#ffff00]\[Arrows][/color]: move and fire
[color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color]: jump
[color=#ffff00]\[Ctrl][/color]: stay put (aim)

[b]Objective:[/b]
Defeat the Bumble Beep








Press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] or [color=#00ff00](A)[/color] to start...

[b]Gamepad controls:[/b]
[color=#00ff00](D-Pad)[/color]: move and fire
[color=#00ff00](A)[/color]: jump
[color=#00ff00](RB)[/color]: stay put (aim)
